Here are the key changes needed:
1. Implement refresh token rotation (new token on each refresh)
2. Add replay detection (revoke entire family if used token is reused)
3. Add family validation (check revokedFamilies)
4. Add absolute lifetime (90 days from family creation)
5. Reduce access token lifetime to 5 minutes
6. Add audit logging

